location.fullValue: The Arbor Plan, Windgate At Carrigan Lake

data.description: Move right into this gorgeous Montrose house with fabulous views and tons of natural light. This two story on an oversized lot with three spacious bedrooms upstairs. There is a private 3/4 owners bathroom and a full bath in the hallway. The main floor provides an open concept living and dining area and a mudroom with laundry off the garage entry. The walk out basement is ready for your sweat equity. Add a family room, bedroom and bathroom when you're ready!
